import { Dropdown, DropdownTrigger, DropdownMenu, 
    DropdownContent, DropdownDivider, DropdownItem, Icon } from 'bloomer';

export default function DropOptions() {
    <Dropdown>
        <DropdownTrigger>
            <Icon isSize='small' className='fas fa-ellipsis-v'/>
        </DropdownTrigger>
        <DropdownMenu>
            <DropdownContent>
                <DropdownItem>Item 1</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Item 2</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Item 3</DropdownItem>
            </DropdownContent>
        </DropdownMenu>
    </Dropdown>

}
